Program: Omnibus
Title: Protocols of the Elders of Zion
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jxw
Last Broadcast Date: 29 September 1990
"Badly written, difficult to read and complete nonsense". A look at the antisemetic hoax, originating in Russia in 1903 which was championed by Henry Ford and Hitler and contributed to ideas of an international Jewish conspiracy.